      "text": "\n\n\n\n\n\n",
      "url": "/articles/startup-founders-embrace-409a-cuts-to-gain-recruiting-edge"
    },
    {
      "text": "\n\nStartup Founders Embrace 409A Cuts to Gain Recruiting Edge\n\n",
      "url": "/articles/startup-founders-embrace-409a-cuts-to-gain-recruiting-edge"
    },
    {
      "text": "\nBetween 2016 and 2021, investors boosted the valuation of Sendbird, a communications software startup, to $1.1 billion, from $6.5 million.\n",
      "url": "/articles/startup-founders-embrace-409a-cuts-to-gain-recruiting-edge"
    },
    {
      "text": "\n\n\n\n\n\n",
      "url": "/articles/the-big-contradiction-at-the-heart-of-the-tech-downturn"
    },
    {
      "text": "\n\nThe Big Contradiction at the Heart of the Tech Downturn\n\n",
      "url": "/articles/the-big-contradiction-at-the-heart-of-the-tech-downturn"
    },
    {
      "text": "\nI\u2019ve read a lot of advice venture capitalists have given founders on the current state of the markets.\n",
      "url": "/articles/the-big-contradiction-at-the-heart-of-the-tech-downturn"
    },
    {
      "text": "\n\n\n\n\n\n",
      "url": "/articles/oracle-discussed-laying-off-thousands-of-workers"
    },
    {
      "text": "\n\nOracle Discussed Laying Off Thousands of Workers\n\n",
      "url": "/articles/oracle-discussed-laying-off-thousands-of-workers"
    },
    {
      "text": "\nOracle recently considered cost reductions of up to $1 billion that could result in thousands of layoffs as soon as August, said a person with direct knowledge of the situation.\n",
      "url": "/articles/oracle-discussed-laying-off-thousands-of-workers"
    },
    {
      "text": "\n\n\n\n\n\n",
      "url": "/articles/bird-nikola-and-other-cash-hungry-spac-targets-ink-novel-share-sales"
    },
    {
      "text": "\n\nWhen Your SPAC Dreams Fail, a Financing of Last Resort\n\n",
      "url": "/articles/bird-nikola-and-other-cash-hungry-spac-targets-ink-novel-share-sales"
    },
    {
      "text": "\nSeveral electric vehicle and mobility startups went public and raised money in the past two years by merging with special purpose acquisition companies.\n",
      "url": "/articles/bird-nikola-and-other-cash-hungry-spac-targets-ink-novel-share-sales"
    },
    {
      "text": "\n\n\n\n",
      "url": "/articles/andreessen-horowitz-thrive-go-bargain-hunting-for-beaten-down-stocks"
    },
    {
      "text": "\n\nAndreessen Horowitz, Thrive Go Bargain Hunting for Beaten-Down Tech Stocks\n\n",
      "url": "/articles/andreessen-horowitz-thrive-go-bargain-hunting-for-beaten-down-stocks"
    },
    {
      "text": "\nPlunging shares of tech stocks have prompted venture capital firms to take an unusual step: buying publicly traded stocks.\n",
      "url": "/articles/andreessen-horowitz-thrive-go-bargain-hunting-for-beaten-down-stocks"
    },
    {
      "text": "\n\n\n\n\n\n",
      "url": "/articles/metas-top-ad-sales-executive-faces-uphill-battle-in-post-sandberg-era"
    },
    {
      "text": "\n\nMeta\u2019s Top Ad Sales Executive Faces Uphill Battle in Post-Sandberg Era\n\n",
      "url": "/articles/metas-top-ad-sales-executive-faces-uphill-battle-in-post-sandberg-era"
    },
    {
      "text": "\nThis week, three Meta Platforms executives will head to the Sun Valley conference in Idaho to woo advertisers: Chief Executive Officer Mark Zuckerberg, Chief Operating Officer Sheryl Sandberg and Chief Business Officer Marne Levine, a key deputy of Sandberg who will be put to the test when the COO leaves the company this fall.\n",
      "url": "/articles/metas-top-ad-sales-executive-faces-uphill-battle-in-post-sandberg-era"
    },
